1.首先创建一个长度是5的数组
然后给数组的每一位赋予随机整数
通过for循环，遍历数组，找出最小的一个值出来

```java
public class temp {

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		int[] array=new int[5];
		int T;
		for(int i=0;i<array.length;i++) {
			array[i]=(int)(Math.random()*100);
		}
		for(int i=0;i<array.length;i++) {
			System.out.print(array[i]+" ");
			
		}
		T=array[0];
		for(int j=1;j<array.length;j++) {
			if(array[j]<=T) {
				T=array[j];
			}
		}
	    System.out.println();
		System.out.println(T);

	}

}
```
2.首先创建一个长度是5的数组,并填充随机数。 (向数组填充随机数的办法，参考这里)

使用for循环或者while循环，对这个数组实现反转效果
```java
package temp;

public class temp {

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		int[] array=new int[5];
		int T;
		for(int i=0;i<array.length;i++) {
			array[i]=(int)(Math.random()*100);
		}
		for(int i=0;i<array.length;i++) {
			System.out.print(array[i]+" ");
			
		}
		System.out.println();
		int[] Array=new int[5];
		for(int i=0,j=array.length-1;j>=0;j--,i++) {
			Array[i]=array[j];
		}
		for(int i=0;i<Array.length;i++)
		   System.out.print(Array[i]+" ");

	}

}

```
3.定义一个5X5的二维数组。 然后使用随机数填充该二维数组。
找出这个二维数组里，最大的那个值，并打印出其二维坐标

```java
public class temp {

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		int[][] array=new int[5][5];
		System.out.println();
		for(int i=0;i<array.length;i++) {
			for(int j=0;j<array[0].length;j++) {
				array[i][j]=(int)(Math.random()*100);
			}
		}
		for(int i=0;i<array.length;i++) {
			for(int each:array[i]) {
				System.out.print(each +" ");
			}
			if(i%5==0) {
				System.out.println();
			}
		}
//		for(int each:array[]) {
//			System.out.println(each);
//		}
	}

}
```

4.Create a program that will randomly select four cards from a deck.

![no.2][no.2]
![no.3][no.3]

```java
package qusetion;

/**
 * @Author yanghao
 * @Create Date 2021-04-27-1:40 PM
 */
public class DeckOfCards {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int[] deck=new int[52];
        String[] suits={"Spades","Hearts","Diamonds","Clubs"};
        String[] ranks={"Ace","2","3","4","5","6","7","8","9","10"
        ,"Jack","Queen","King"};

        //Initialize the cards
        for(int i=0;i<deck.length;i++){
            deck[i]=i;
        }

        //Shuffle the cards
        for(int i=0;i<deck.length;i++){
            //Generate an index j
            int j=(int)(Math.random()*deck.length);
            int temp=deck[j];
            deck[j]=deck[i];
            deck[i]=temp;
        }

        //Display the first four cards
        for(int i=0;i<4;i++){
            String suit=suits[deck[i]/13];
            String rank=ranks[deck[i]%13];
            System.out.println("Card: "+rank+" of "+suit);
        }
    }
}

```
